description:
In episode 954, Jack and Miles are joined by We Need to Talk About Britney's Jen Zaborowski to discuss positive covid cases at the Olympics, the Delta variant wave, Fox News jumping shit, an Israeli surveillance software being used for evil, the end of salad bars, Britney Spears, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Coco Gauff Out of Olympics After Positive COVID-19 Test as Cases in Athletes’ Village Grow
  2. Kara Eaker, U.S. Women’s Alternate Olympic Gymnast, Tests Positive for COVID in Tokyo Chaos
  3. The Uncanny Delta Wave
  4. Steve Doocy: Get the COVID-19 vaccine if you have chance, it will 'save your life'
  5. Revealed: leak uncovers global abuse of cyber-surveillance weapon
  6. Why salad bars may never come back
  7. Britney Spears' Bodyguard Claims She Was Fed Antipsychotic Drugs That Would Make Her 'Go From Sane To Talking About Parallel Universes': Report
